quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  38,21,"Hara kumpital wenjunooЙ“e Й“en arii maa, nde Й“e Жҙawunoo ka ganngunal"
  38,22,"Nde Й“e naatuoo ka Daawuuda, o Й—enЖҙii Й“e. ЖҒe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu ! Ko wennjuЙ“e Й—iЙ—o; goЙ—Й—o e amen tooГұii oya. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde amen, wata a tooГұu, tinndinaa men e laawol focciingol ngol"
  38,23,"Oo ko musiЙ—Й—o am: himo jogii baali cappanЙ—e jeenay e jeenay, min miЙ—o jogii baalii gootii. O wi'i: \"Henndinam ngii\"; o foolimi e yewtere"
  38,24,"O maaki: \"Pellet, o tooГұirii ma lamndagol baalii maa ngii, waЙ—tugol e baali makko Й—in\". ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko hawtuЙ“e tooГұindirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i - Й“en non no fanЙ—i. - Daawuuda felliti, wonnde Men jarribike mo. O insinanii Joomi makko, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubi"
  38,25,"Men yaafanii mo Й—um. Pellet non, hino woodani mo ko Amen, Й“adal e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde"
  38,26,"Ko an yo Daawuuda, Men waЙ—ii ma lomto ka leydi. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e, sakko Й—e majjine e laawol Allah ngol\". Pellet, Й“en majjooЙ“e e laawol Allah ngol, hino woodani Й“e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e yejjitiri kon, Г‘alaande hasboore nden"
  38,27,"Men tagiraali kammu ngun e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji kon, meere. ЖҠum ko sikke yedduЙ“e Й“en. Bone woodanii Й“en yedduЙ“e, e Yiite ngen"
  38,28,"Ka Men waЙ—ay Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙi, wano bonnooЙ“e Й“en ka hoore leydi? Kaa Men waЙ—ay gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, wano faajireeЙ“e Й“en"
  38,29,"Ko Deftere barkinaande, woni ko Men jippini e maaЙ—a, fii no Й“e taskora Aayeeje mayre, e ko joomiraaЙ“e haqqille Й“en waajitora"
  38,30,"Men yeЙ—i Daawuuda Sulaymaana, - jeyaaЙ—o moЖҙЖҙo - Ko o Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o tuubugol-ruttoo"
  38,31,"Janto nde o hollanoo kiikiiЙ—e, pucci yooЙ—uЙ—i yaawuЙ—i"
  38,32,"o maaki: \"Min Й“urnorii yiЙ—ugol jawdi, dii ko mi jantotoo Joomi am kon, haa [naange] ngen mutoyii"
  38,33,"Ruttee lam Й—i\". O woni e sodugol Й—i ka taape e ka daaЙ—e"
  38,34,"GomЙ—ii Men jarribike Sulaymaana, Men werlii e jullere makko nden Й“anndu. Refti o tuubi"
  38,35,"O maaki: \"Joomi am, haforanam, yeЙ—aa lam laamu, ngu heertantaako goЙ—Й—o goo, Й“aawo am. Pellet, ko An woni yeЙ—oowo On"
  38,36,"Men eltani mo henndu ndun, tawi hindu wifira e sago makko, neweende, nokku kala ko o yiЙ—i"
  38,37,"E seytanuuji Й—in, mahaynooЙ—i e mutaynooЙ—i"
  38,38,"GoЙ—Й—i Й—in, ko dummbaaЙ—i e penЙ—e"
  38,39,"ЖҠum ko dokkal Amen. Okkitir, maa jogitoraa ko aldaa e lamnditoreede"
  38,40,"Ko pellet, hino woodani mo ka Amen, Й“adal e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde"
  38,41,"Janto kadi jeyaaЙ—o Amen on Ayyuuba, nde o noddunoo Joomi makko, wonnde : \"Seytaane memirii lam tampere e muuseendi"
  38,42,"[Allah wi'ani mo]: \"Latir tunndawal maa ngal [ka leydi]: ЖҠam Й—oo, ko lootorЙ—am, Й“uuЙ“uЙ—al e njaram"
  38,43,"Men yeЙ—i mo Й“eynguure makko nden, e yeru maЙ“Й“e tawti Й“e, yurmeende immorde e Amen, e waaju wonannde marЙ“e haqqille Й“en"
  38,44,"Nanngir sookewo maa ngon, tamere huЙ—o, piyiraa Й—um [suddiiЙ—o maa on], fii wata a firtu (woondoore nden)\". Men tawu mo, muГұГұiiЙ—o. O moЖҙЖҙii jeyaaЙ—o. Pellet, ko o Й—uuЙ—uЙ—o tuubugol-ruttoo"
  38,45,"Janto kadi, jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, Ibraahiima e Ishaaqa e Yaaquuba, joomiraaЙ“e cemmbe e yi'anЙ—e"
  38,46,"Men heertinanii Й“e heertinannde, annditugol galle (laakara) Й—en"
  38,47,"E kadi Й“ee ka Amen, ko jeyaaЙ“e e suЙ“aaЙ“e moЖҙЖҙuЙ“e suЙ“aaЙ“e"
  38,48,"Janto kadi Ismaa'iila, e Yuusa'u, e Zal-Kifli, kala maЙ“Й“e, ko jeyaaЙ“e e suЙ“aaЙ“e"
  38,49,"ЖҠum ko waaju. Ko pellet, hino woodani gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en, ruttorde moЖҙЖҙunde"
  38,50,"ЖҠum ko Aljannaaji ГұiiЙ“al, Й—i Й“e udditanaa dame mun"
  38,51,"hara ko Й“e soЙ“Й“indii Й“e ton, hiЙ“e nodda ton muuyanteeЙ—i Й—uuЙ—uЙ—i e njaram"